{% comment %}
Variant ID: DB-EDM-EXP-20260625-EDITORIAL-V1
Status: Candidate experiment, testing. Not a standard base.
Mode: Exploration.
Brand: Diveblues.
Template type: Brand-editorial Shopify Email custom Liquid.

Effects tested:
- Personalized opening with customer.first_name default fallback.
- Editorial hero with Shopify Files placeholder image and live-text fallback.
- Cool / clean / bright Diveblues color bands with solid bgcolor fallback.
- Two-column editorial table modules that stack on mobile when supported.
- Static placeholder product cards. No product variable dependency in v1.
- Temporary branded footer with required unsubscribe URL.
- Dark-mode fallback using solid backgrounds and explicit text colors.

Placeholders to replace:
- All https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0000/0000/files/... image URLs.
- All PLACEHOLDER_LINK_* URLs.
- Static product names, microcopy, and CTA destinations.
- Support/social links in the temporary footer.
- Physical mailing address in the footer (required by CAN-SPAM before real send).
- Open tracking: keep {{ open_tracking }} if open tracking is enabled. If Shopify rejects it and tracking is confirmed disabled, remove only after documenting the decision.

How to paste:
1. Open Shopify Email.
2. Add or edit a custom Liquid section.
3. Paste this whole template.
4. Replace placeholder URLs and copy.
5. Save, send a test email, and record results in outputs/diveblues/edm/templates/index.md.

Test checklist:
- Gmail, Outlook, Apple Mail.
- Mobile viewport.
- Dark mode.
- Image-off rendering.
- CTA links.
- Unsubscribe link.
- File size under 50KB for this custom Liquid section.

Pending variable verification:
- all_products[handle] / product variables are not used in this v1 template.
- customer.accepts_marketing is not used in this v1 template.
{% endcomment %}

